sequenceDiagram
    actor Player
    participant System
    
    Note over Player, System: UC-04: Take Item
    Player->>System: clickItem(item)
    System-->>Player: showActionMenu(item)
    Player->>System: selectAction("TAKE")
    System->>System: checkInventorySpace()
    
    alt Inventory has empty slot
        System->>System: addItemToInventory(item)
        System->>System: removeItemFromMap(item)
        System-->>Player: close action menu and update UI
    else Inventory is full
        System-->>Player: show "Take" option grayed out
    end